**Descriptions of .exe files**

-- Cygwin.exe --
A Linux shell environment for Windows. Required for developers who need to run MontiDroid build scripts (make, bash, git, etc.) natively on Windows systems. Tested on Windows 7 and above.

---> COMING SOON <---
Additional tooling – too many to list individually. Highlights will include:
- ARM cross‑compiler wrapper for Windows hosts
- Automated partitioning tool for bootloader flashing
- Signature verifier for MontiDroid boot images
- Hardware diagnostic interface (Signal 41 compatible)

Stay tuned for updates in the `tools/win32/` folder.
